OL,3,CWealthiest Channel Islanders revealed
OL,4,Cin The Sunday Times Rich List
OL,6,FFive Channel Island billionaires have
OL,7,Fbeen named in this year's Sunday Times
OL,8,FRich List.
OL,10,FJersey's Glenn Gordon and his family,
OL,11,Fwho own spirits company William Grant
OL,12,F& Sons, top the local rankings.
OL,14,FThey are worth more than #5.6bn,
OL,15,Fhaving increased their wealth by #1bn
OL,16,Fin the past year.
