OL,3,CWealthiest Channel Islanders revealed
OL,4,Cin The Sunday Times Rich List
OL,6,FChris and Sarah Dawson came second,
OL,7,Fjumping 15 places on the Rich List,
OL,8,Fwith their #2.5bn fortune mainly
OL,9,Fsecured through their retail brand,
OL,10,FThe Range.
OL,12,FThe list also includes Specsavers
OL,13,Ffounders Douglas and Dame Mary Perkins
OL,14,F- Guernsey's richest family - as well
OL,15,Fas Steve Lansdown, who founded Bristol
OL,16,FSport.
OL,18,FFounder of the website
OL,19,FMoneysupermarket, Simon Nixon, came
OL,20,Fthird.
